{"tid":1551079,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[長文教學] 同我立即買支可以自動Back up上Cloud既Cam保護自己!!!最平40蚊都有!","createTime":"2019-09-07T23:02:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-08T23:19:42.000Z","uid":69864,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"a30f71ac80c9324dfc6366d7331086b08d24d424","tid":1551079,"uid":69864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T23:02:43.000Z","msg":"香港人,<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔想被自殺? 唔想比黑警老屈? 想幫兄弟搜證?</span></span><br />\n係時候幫自己屋企裝返幾支CCTV<br />\n起碼,一支對屋企窗外樓下,一支對屋企裡面<br />\n<br />\n重點係,一定要個CCTV係support 「cloud」功能<br />\n自動幫你經網路back up上網,<br />\n就算黑警入到黎爆你門破壞你cctv都好,你網上都有留底<br />\n同埋一啲唔係對住你會換衫同暴露太多自己私隱既cam<br />\n一定要share個back UP雲端比你身邊信任得過既人<br />\n因為就算被自殺,都要拍得班惡鬼做過既事,用黎證明自己唔係自殺,係被謀殺!<br />\n唔好只係比家人,仲要比信任得過既朋友! 因為隨時同你黎個滅聲全家筒。<br />\n當朋友同你聯絡唔到,入你Cloud就可以睇到你安唔安全。<br />\n<br />\n進階既巴打絲打可以考慮玩 無線+太陽能cctv <br />\nSet係公眾場所一啲死角位, 定期去收集影片,<br />\n但起碼一支cam成七八千銀, 所以有錢有心既人先好咁做。<br />\n==============================================<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">以下我提供小小方法比大家,如果大家有建議都歡迎大家提供下,最好唔好係大陸牌子,特別係用QR code登入果種。</div><br />\n==============================================<br />\n方法1. 隨意Ipcam +一部連網既電腦上面安裝 <ins>DVR.Webcam</ins>  難易度:中低<br />\n成本: ~200蚊左右平既IPcam + 80蚊買程式 + onedrive/googledrive/dropbox/icloud月費<br />\n(當然你可以用free 15GB定期清理,但都可以考慮入手一個無)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bnEmtht.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbnEmtht.jpg&h=cf9bab59&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n==============================================<br />\n方法2. 隨意Ipcam + 舊手機 + Onvif ip camera monitor <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Pro</span></span> 難易度:中<br />\n成本: ~200蚊IPcam + 27蚊升級做Pro版 + Googledrive 月費/15GB<br />\n(好處係有部手機就做到,但呢個APP好似只可以GOOGLE DRIVE)<br />\n教學:<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"https://www.ipcent.com/home/articles/how-to-use-google_drive-for-onvifer-cloud-storage\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ipcent.com%2Fhome%2Farticles%2Fhow-to-use-google_drive-for-onvifer-cloud-storage&d=N8yyMuQB0XA0Wgs8sIkprs5qU0izJB5q5dcgVJazxes%3D&h=b5ce7743\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ipcent.com/home/articles/how-to-use-google_drive-for-onvifer-cloud-storage</a></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SaXvmFP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSaXvmFP.png&h=507be392&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n==============================================<br />\n方法3. 直接買部有Cloud服務提供既閉路,例如NETGEAR ARLO 之類  難易度:最低 但簡錢偏貴<br />\n成本 = 500蚊到8000蚊不都有既CAM + 要比固定月費去用佢功能<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tQCrEzP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtQCrEzP.png&h=a6779637&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n用呢個方法大家小心出事,因為好多平IPCAM都係產自大陸,例如VSTARCAM<br />\n所以如果大家要係腦場買隻有付費CLOUD 功能既IPCAM, 真係要避大陸牌子<br />\n如果唔係佢地有留BACK DOOR,同埋佢地可以查個Cloud既video既話,<br />\n你只會係大陸天眼既一份子<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">同埋... 記得轉密碼呀支cam!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!</span></strong></span><br />\n==============================================<br />\n方法4. 電腦+usb眼仔+google drive自動back up 軟件+定時錄影程式  難易度: 識用電腦就得<br />\n成本: 普通電腦鋪幾十蚊眼仔 + google drive/其他有軟件版既Back up drive 既錢<br />\n唔撚理,拉條長usb線去角落頭24小時開電腦對撚住個門口影住佢,但有風險就係佢有機會可以係你upload之前就關你機! 所以唔太建議!<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com/intl/zh-TW_ALL/drive/download/backup-and-sync/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Fintl%2Fzh-TW_ALL%2Fdrive%2Fdownload%2Fbackup-and-sync%2F&d=N8yyMuQB0XA0Wgs8sIkprs5qU0izJB5q5dcgVJazxes%3D&h=0d203bf1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/intl/zh-TW_ALL/drive/download/backup-and-sync/</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8JuYvFZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8JuYvFZ.png&h=1a5d64d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n============================================== <br />\n方法5. Youtube直播+usb眼仔+電腦按鍵精靈12個鐘就重新stream一次 難易度: 中偏高<br />\n成本: usb眼仔幾十蚊左右<br />\n首先你要識用youtube直播, 其次就係你要識錄按精,<br />\n因為youtube live時限係12小時, 所以你要自動化既話,就要識寫腳本去自動化on live既電腦流程<br />\n但呢個就係最平既做法,同埋live係有即時保障<br />\n而且好重要既一點係,你電腦千祈唔好登入youtube/Google account !<br />\n因為佢可以上你後台刪你片,你只需要記住你直播頁既地址就夠!<br />\n簡單講,你只需要定期12個鐘就斷5分鐘live,再向呢個固定既youtube地址射video上去就ok!<br />\nlike this:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pP0HXtw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpP0HXtw.png&h=127d3ab0&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7TZhMjO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7TZhMjO.jpg&h=3c799530&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n===============================================<br />\n<br />\n就算手足唔幫手Set支對外既,<br />\n都立即同我SET返支係屋企保護下自己!<br />\n我唔想再見到有人無神神有手足自殺! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">呢個應該係我第一次想求大家幫我推一推既Post<br />\n只希望我只係諗多左,無手足會再被自殺,大家要活到可以除低面罩既最後</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16ee167bee442cad1c36bbe7ecbaf9eee8729070","tid":1551079,"uid":289846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T23:04:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46d73814e3ce7ecc43b199910719110ac9d9a3a0","tid":1551079,"uid":69864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T23:04:25.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"05cd0fe95c8b45d20993960388798c202454cd70","tid":1551079,"uid":69864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T23:06:41.000Z","msg":"9<br />\n更正一點,上面有句斷左<br />\n原文係(當然你可以用free 15GB定期清理,但都可以考慮入手一個無)<br />\n改正後:(當然你可以用free 15GB定期清理,但都可以考慮入手一個無限空間既google drive,keywords is G-Suit/大專google drive)"},{"pid":"70b0a6bec73dc0bae7de2a88579df809e53ede2e","tid":1551079,"uid":88287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T23:13:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e607662049026d919343f7b1c0302367ec41dd4b","tid":1551079,"uid":69864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T23:21:28.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"7c1267aa2a092e9449d03505d90fc4ce12ea909a","tid":1551079,"uid":69864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T23:43:22.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"cc5958ce2f2b69ef34e920e7c255d7f189035f6e","tid":1551079,"uid":304734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T23:44:36.000Z","msg":"wish"},{"pid":"a0a00041128e6657ef7636d2a882be9616245503","tid":1551079,"uid":69864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T00:10:05.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"c96b4b7ca95d1c7047aa35c9574ed59cd019037e","tid":1551079,"uid":158404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T00:11:32.000Z","msg":"岩啊 保障自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2a6edd6461d499de2b48b9fb8476db95055b462","tid":1551079,"uid":217949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T00:39:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c0c097310715c0890d31fa717e4a009164aa233d","tid":1551079,"uid":227174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T00:43:35.000Z","msg":"前線必須品, 推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"751d23fe2172fba1660e912d3a775ff7044eefad","tid":1551079,"uid":69864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T00:49:45.000Z","msg":"我係被捕人士 想同啲自殺傾向嘅手足講兩句<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1550837\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1550837</a>"},{"pid":"3f5735e3dd5678a5a0dc7dfb086923311571f044","tid":1551079,"uid":102187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T02:36:13.000Z","msg":"ip cam 有咩牌子推介? 唔想要大陸野"},{"pid":"01d750231fc733f2d5cb3077dcdcd88e41cd0800","tid":1551079,"uid":24506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T02:37:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c77f3ae5fa48cc6b0fa887c5ee1eaa914925bcf1","tid":1551079,"uid":69864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3f5735e3dd5678a5a0dc7dfb086923311571f044","tid":1551079,"uid":102187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T02:36:13.000Z","msg":"ip cam 有咩牌子推介? 唔想要大陸野"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T03:15:27.000Z","msg":"我都係上網睇<br />\nReolink 好似有得直接用佢自家月費cloud<br />\n但佢官網冇寫香港用得,所以唔知work唔work<br />\n但最差既結果我估係你買完返黎都可以當普通ip cam用<br />\n留名睇食用報告<br />\n<br />\n至於NETGEAR獨立出黎既 Arlo 應該係IPCAM界既寶馬<br />\n相對安全同配套高, 但同寶馬一樣, 好撚貴 , 貴到成皮既都有。<br />\n<br />\nBTW TP-LINK好似都有出, 你唔放心大陸貨既話可以試下TP-LINK自家IP CAM"},{"pid":"0fd070aa473065cb5ab17d15b8d5ebfb13248c9b","tid":1551079,"uid":69864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T03:21:42.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"7517451256b47845862f2e0eb568f8bd44bccd6c","tid":1551079,"uid":69864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T03:44:18.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"c66c74b26c4cb80424290e5f56e3d53982714ec5","tid":1551079,"uid":9448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T03:55:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f0cefc3ced8c5a3610e8737e1edba7e2543b824d","tid":1551079,"uid":69864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T05:37:54.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"92e013b39ea4492d2a85c3c4b7642c79c9457e19","tid":1551079,"uid":69864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T05:55:05.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"21a570816f56930d347fed5ddf886f072bd6d08c","tid":1551079,"uid":69864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T06:27:29.000Z","msg":"1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"463c2ce085712fb853faa62ce3902d29167dc38f","tid":1551079,"uid":69864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T06:56:51.000Z","msg":"LAST PUSH , 各位自重, 最緊要安全"},{"pid":"a242fa93d223b2500f45b87ccaafca96a3d9cd9a","tid":1551079,"uid":35478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T12:27:13.000Z","msg":"其實一早就諗住買枝放係膊頭影低D警暴<br />\n次次都係度求片<br />\n但廢事比人當係鬼 最後都無買"},{"pid":"a085e96e97dc7560b68d6355dd6928c7bb550e4c","tid":1551079,"uid":69864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a242fa93d223b2500f45b87ccaafca96a3d9cd9a","tid":1551079,"uid":35478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T12:27:13.000Z","msg":"其實一早就諗住買枝放係膊頭影低D警暴<br />\n次次都係度求片<br />\n但廢事比人當係鬼 最後都無買"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T22:56:14.000Z","msg":"其實呢個真心奇怪左好耐<br />\n點解唔好好隱藏自己面容<br />\n反而去怪責人影自己<br />\n遮面領巾加頂帽真係買唔起咩大家<br />\n阻礙資訊流通在我而言絕對唔係一件好事"}]}